parcel.name: 3DVoxelPunks Gallery
parcel.description: Only 100 3DVoxelPunks will be created. All NFT's will come with an unlockable IPFS file which includes a headshot .png, rotating GIF, and 3D .vox file which can be brought into .vox-based games such as Cryptovoxels (not currently as a wearable).

features.text:
#3DVoxelPunks are sculptures for the Metaverse. Only 100 will ever be created.

#3DVoxelPunk Wearables are identities for the metaverse. They can only be created by request from official CryptoPunk owners

#Visit our site below to request your 3DVoxelPunk Wearable.

#Not affiliated with Larva Labs.
